### Failover Configuration
@baseUrl = https://api.costkatana.com/api
@apiKey = your_api_key

### Get Failover Config
GET {{baseUrl}}/failover/config
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Update Failover Config
PUT {{baseUrl}}/failover/config
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"enabled": true, "providers": ["openai", "anthropic"]}

### Test Failover
POST {{baseUrl}}/failover/test
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"primaryProvider": "openai"}
